<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,616,791,817]" pageId="8" pageNumber="17">
Key to Afrotropical species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hermann" authorityYear="1905" box="[528,616,791,817]" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Perasis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
